# Enforce LF (Unix/Linux-style line endings) for all text files
# Ensures consistency across platforms, avoiding issues
# caused by mixed formats (e.g., CRLF on Windows vs. LF on Unix/Linux/macOS).
#
# - `* text=auto`: Detect text files automatically.
# - `eol=lf`: Force LF format on checkout and commit.
#
# Applies to all files. Add specific rules below if needed.
* text=auto eol=lf